_sText:
Triggy and I worked on this map for about 4 days. We have created a gg map, which takes place in an underpass at midnight. Barrels and crates that have been dumped into the underpass from above make for good cover. With two platforms at each spawn that offer a vantage point over the underpass.

Note: This is Micro Version, the will be an extended version coming soon. Hope you enjoy our work!

**My First Release on FPSB. <3
